* memory-access: miss aligned access (CUDA C textbook)
* stream-gpu: STREAM for GPU with OpenACC, OpenMP, and KOKKOS
* omptarget-cuda: OpenMP Target + CUDA
* p2p-gpus: peer-to-peer access between GPUs in a node.
* tensorcore: examples of using tensorcore
* spmv/mm: sparse matrix
* mlpack: some benchmark using mlpack (https://github.com/mlpack/mlpack)
* mini-apps: miniture applications (MD, FFT part of plane-wave DFT, etc.)
